resources.name: Search a movie by id
resources.description:
The route searches for movie details on https://developers.themoviedb.org/ and returns the content if it exists. The content is persisted on the local basis.

Path Parameters:

movide_id : integer  ||* required ||  The movie id to search.


Query String: 

language: string  || optional ||  Language of the response (en-US, pt-BR ...).

append_to_response: || string (optional) ||  Accept up to 2 values  separated by comma  (videos,images)


RESPONSES:

200: Sucess, returns de movie details

404:  “Movie_id does not exists”
